          <Data name="Type">
            <value>Event</value>
          </Data>
          <Data name="Description">
            <value>Several hundred gay men from the
              Golden Horseshoe area attended a gala, open-air bottle party held at the home of
              Robert C. Hart, 63 Highcliffe Avenue. The
              party was raided by the police, who complained of noise, and the guests were
              forced to leave. 
